x%C3%BAc-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-ch%E1%BB%AD-h%C3%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-h%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-t%E1%BA%A5t-thanh-th%E1%BA%A7n-khi%E1%BB%83n-n%E1%BB%AF-n%C3%B4-A-Kh%E1%BB%83-ki%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%AD-A/poem-bUL1a0_VuBSDmlZEAArY5w">Thu hành quan trương vọng đốc xúc đông chử háo đạo hướng tất thanh thần, khiển nữ nô A Khể, kiên tử A Đoàn vãng vấn - 秋行官張望督促東渚耗稻向畢清晨遣女奴阿稽豎子阿段往問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-nguy%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1-d%E1%BB%AF-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-tho%E1%BA%A1i-C%E1%BB%91-S%C6%A1n-C%E1%BB%91-nh%C3%A2n/poem-PSGmrGmn-mQnYjSbU9SJ8Q">Trường An nguyệt dạ dữ hữu nhân thoại Cố Sơn - Cố nhân - 長安月夜與友人話故山－故人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-3U8mtpWIAHhj1X7f-gybnw">Trường tương tư kỳ 1 - 長相思其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%C3%AAn-Ch%C3%ADnh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87n-tho%C3%A1i-tri%E1%BB%81u-v%C3%A3n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BA%A3-d%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-1UcGf_h-gj2sC-6_apfE0g">Tuyên Chính điện thoái triều vãn xuất tả dịch - 宣政殿退朝晚出左掖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
